(20411, 10292, 2227, 4, '相信 and I BELIEVE     / feat special rapper', '從intro開始\r\n去感受 很不一樣的搖滾...\r\n\r\n當時 最令陳浩感動的作品\r\n耗時2年\r\n\r\n此版本為初定版\r\n搭配周杰倫功夫灌籃主題曲rapper沈懿\r\n\r\n試聽開放長度至2:47快把握機會開放1天\r\n\r\n', '2010-01-01 00:00:00', 0000, 50, 0, 1, '相信 and I BELIEVE \r\n詞曲編曲製作錄音/ 陳浩 XhenHow \r\n中文rap/沈懿 陳浩\r\n\r\nI believe\r\n當我遇見你\r\n像溫暖陽光 \r\n照亮我的心\r\n\r\nAnd I believe\r\n就這麼神奇 \r\n把我交給你\r\n投入你懷裡\r\n\r\noh can''t you Ssee\r\n多少的風雨\r\n恐怖的絕情\r\n吞噬我的心\r\n\r\noh can''t you see\r\n滾燙的淚滴\r\n不安的寂靜\r\n動搖我信心\r\n\r\n\r\nand I BELIEVE\r\nand I BELIEVE\r\ndeny the night\r\n擊潰這空虛\r\n\r\nand I BELIEVE\r\nand I BELIEVE\r\n邁向光明\r\n不再猶豫\r\n因為有你\r\n\r\n【Rap】\r\ni believe i can do it\r\ni believe i can make it\r\ni believe i can beat it\r\nthe devil never stop me\r\n\r\nplease give me give me some happeness\r\nplease stop the children crying\r\nplease just trush me trush me.\r\ncove me! stop  the wrong thing\r\n\r\ntired of being what you want me to be\r\neverything feel so far away from me\r\ni need to remember just to breathe\r\ni need you to stay away from me\r\n\r\n【沈懿- RAP】\r\nI BELIEVE 挺胸立定\r\n眼神堅定  寶貴的不只勝利\r\n\r\n來吧同心協力  姊妹兄弟\r\n風暴將來臨  我替你遮蔽\r\n\r\n不到最後一秒掌聲都不放棄\r\n我們全力相挺爭取你的榮譽\r\n\r\n相信  將所有心都凝聚\r\n信不信  未見之事也有確據\r\n\r\n人民重燃熱火高聲歌唱\r\n旌旗飄揚故鄉土地之上\r\n\r\n有家人在我不怕  \r\n同胞的期望化作無窮力量\r\n\r\n我踏  我向上  我有夢想  就在那前方\r\n帶我衝破那羅網 \r\n我們的泉源在天上\r\n更快更高更遠  超過所求所想\r\n\r\n【陳浩-RAP】\r\ni believe i can do it\r\ni believe i can make it\r\ni believe i can beat it\r\nthe devil never stop me\r\n\r\nplease give me give me some happeness\r\nplease stop the children crying\r\nplease just trush me! trush me!\r\ncove me! stop  the wrong thing\r\n', '', 246, '', '陳浩 Xhen How', '陳浩 Xhen How', '陳浩 Xhen How', '陳浩 Xhen How Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2009-12-28 02:00:18', '2015-03-12 13:40:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
