(20381, 12753, 2219, 12, 'Choke Up (Why) (Recorded by Loc&Hostile&Soulreal-X&Tai) (Demo)', 'It''s very lucky to work with Hostile,really exciting.His appearing filled the happiness into the whole studio.''cos of the time,it''s very hurry to finish the song.The lyrics consist of some freestyling and some old ones.But,the excellent performance of Hostile made the beat shine.And we used the classic "Why" of Lapy Crew as a sample,which made the song symbolize some stories.From a little child to a man who is touching the dream,this is all we are doing now.Loc''s beat made Hostile wanna rap with passion.The cooperation shows how different cultures crashed and created together.We identified with each other in simple and straight catharsis.It''s easy to resonate,''cos we are all born for hiphop culture.As we don''t collect many materials,this song must not be too magnificent.But as a hiphop song,it reached the standard.The main meaning of the cooperation is building the relationship and the basis of next work,which will be far more international and famous.\r\n\r\nThanks goes to the people who joined the project,\r\n\r\nTai and Soulreal-X of T.M.Production,Ding Dang of Skip Shadow and the recording engineer,Mr Gao.', '2009-12-25 00:00:00', 2000, 9, 0, 2, '怎么会这么热 怎么会这么渴\r\n我带来的改变永远不会踩刹车\r\n这世界所有人耳朵都饿\r\n不停地想要我的饶舌\r\n放我的歌 空气发热\r\n有我在这 就是要享乐\r\n管它红绿蓝什么颜色\r\n只要又我 就有快乐\r\nHow hot I felt,cos the stage is so hot.\r\nWhat I gon'' do?U came when I come again.\r\nThis morden age hiphop that we said it 嘻哈\r\nU can play guitar while I''m playin'' hiphop.\r\nU know what I mean,man?I ain''t a superstar.\r\nBoy,what a fuckin'' star.\r\nU wanna be that star attractin'' girls in ur club.\r\nHo,boy,u gotta laugh,cos u may be a dog.\r\naYo, whatsup, Ni hao, hi\r\nwo jiao Wang Xiao Shuai\r\nbut mei guan xi\r\nmost nu-har just call me that sexy lao-wai\r\nmy native language skills are so high\r\nEloquent poetry is what I write\r\nemotive imagery that will make you shy\r\nso you cant even look inside my green eye\r\ngo to Vogue look left, look right\r\nsurrounded by thugs dressed in black, but our trainers are white\r\nso when we step we shine bright\r\nsome of us looking for love, but some of us just looking for a fight tonight\r\nwe’re high, \r\nso we look right look left\r\nsee my boy Loc, with the chicks he’s the best\r\nnext\r\nwe bowl to the stage like YO\r\npass the mic- we don’t just rap – we put on a fuckin show\r\nbust\r\nthe crowd loves us to sing to them\r\ncos girls just want to touch that ying-guo-ren\r\nthen we roll on to the next house party\r\nconfident cos lyrically they can''t out smart me\r\ngangs of girls come tryin to grope me\r\nso many chains around my neck its like my jewelers trying to choke me\r\nI get pulled to the side so I slide through the divide\r\nchill with them crazy girls from Chuan mei riiight\r\nchillin at the side, its along-side the stage right\r\nand Loc spies an unsupervised mic,\r\nI’m like\r\nwo tsao’\r\nspot light ignites\r\ncrowd excites\r\nand to your delight\r\nwe recite\r\nand incite some madness then go to the next site\r\nfuck an invite, an fuck being polite\r\nima tsai jing king, he’s a chuan mei knight\r\nfrom Beijing to Shanghai\r\nyou cant stop us aiiiight', '', 252, '', 'Soulreal-X,Logic Loc', 'Logic Loc,Hostile(UK)', 'Logic Loc', 'Lapy Record', '', 0, 0, 0, '2009-12-26 23:14:17', '2015-03-12 13:40:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
